                            <comment id="12455075" author="otis" created="Sat, 2 Dec 2006 05:29:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;analysis.jsp is getting changed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-58&quot; title=&quot;Change Admin components to return XML like the rest of the system&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-58&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-58&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, so the last 3 CSS issues will be taken care of there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12459008" author="hossman" created="Sat, 16 Dec 2006 08:40:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I made the neccessary changes to action.jsp, and analysis.jsp as well (since the analysys.jsp changes in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-58&quot; title=&quot;Change Admin components to return XML like the rest of the system&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-58&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-58&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; were rolled back recently)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i didn&apos;t modify get-file.jsp &amp;#8211; it&apos;s mime type is explicitly text/plain, so there&apos;s nothing to escape. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
